msgid "离线语音VC系列"
msgstr "Offline Voice VC Series"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:17
#: 2b99615aaaf2450ea648761b3936c33d
msgid "语料命令词最多支持多少条？"
msgstr "What is the maximum number of supported command words?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:18
#: 722c2e86148940389f8c729db09d1784
msgid "150条"
msgstr "150 entries."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:22
#: bcfc2978f069464d98a2cb0a927586af
msgid "唤醒词最多支持多少条？"
msgstr "What is the maximum number of supported wake words?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:23
#: 1d2b1eb8a3aa40018dbd67e4a39cee16
msgid "10条"
msgstr "10 entries."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:27
#: b8b880b84f5348a0a2c719edb1041ee5
msgid "VC系列模组电路设计时候，需不需要外加功放芯片？"
msgstr ""
"When designing circuits for VC series modules, is an external power "
"amplifier chip required?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:28
#: 4c72c21465b24ca5909a40676e0ba012
msgid "不需要"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:32
#: d70d351061524365825aeaa5a37fb774
msgid "VC系列模组支持以下哪些烧录方式？"
msgstr "Which programming methods are supported by VC series modules?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:33
#: ace4c3a913a34ffca7bc2c8203c566e8
msgid "JTAG调试器和串口烧录"
msgstr "JTAG debugger and serial port programming"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:37
#: 688f5695dc2349c8892bb5e61dd0f298
msgid "VC系列模组的电压电流要求是？"
msgstr "What are the voltage and current requirements of VC series modules?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:38
#: ae25ed3849d948cb9113f109ee97c448
msgid "供电电压 3.6V-5V，供电电流>500mA"
msgstr "Supply voltage: 3.6V–5V; supply current: >500mA"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:42
#: f758d208a5ee48e5ad6992f51a8a7db8
msgid "中英版本唤醒/命令固件支持自学习吗？"
msgstr ""
"Do the Chinese and English wake-word/command firmware versions support self-"
"learning?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:43
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:74
#: 135407eb6df849baa82b042bde70de8e 758d591479cc4f0fa965dc67ae3597b1
msgid "支持"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:47
#: 69bd8ff90d774311a7f4ebc4f476719e
msgid "支持粤语/河南话等方言吗？"
msgstr "Are Cantonese, Henan dialect, and other dialects supported?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:48
#: ad84d65cbbe2465f831e5f920d6c3c1b
msgid "不支持"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:52
#: cc9aa3599620429b815902bc55e4e2ac
msgid "VC系列和之前的VB系列语音模组，开发环境/下载器是一样的吗？"
msgstr ""
"Are the development environment and downloader for the VC series the same as "
"those for the previous VB series voice modules?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:53
#: cb90f0f24c9e4b97a99d06bd9c6163ad
msgid "VC使用开发平台是Linux ,VB是Windows CDK IDE，各自有自己的下载器下载"
msgstr ""
"VC uses a Linux development platform, while VB uses the Windows CDK IDE. "
"Each has its own downloader."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:57
#: ed9270860d314392a14ff6220986bb2a
msgid "VC系列模组接麦克风推荐购买哪种"
msgstr "What type of microphone is recommended for VC series modules?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:58
#: 031a44e1eb22424ea2c7a1286fb9aad2
msgid "可以按照灵敏度-27db的标准"
msgstr "You can choose one according to the sensitivity standard of -27 dB."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:61
#: c51b6f47d43040cc8d6c6cf258fa7e2c
msgid "VC系列模组咪头的拾音最远能达到多少米"
msgstr ""
"What is the maximum pickup distance of the microphone on VC series modules?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:62
#: b9baceebbbea499da366c70ac11e3308
msgid "最远5米。"
msgstr "Up to 5 meters."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:65
#: 5fb6dfaac9514b8f851b1745bc1dfa5f
msgid "VC系列模组支持播报吗"
msgstr "Do VC series modules support voice announcements?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:66
#: cbd2112ec34349ffaab6550fb36323c5
msgid "支持，不过没有TTS功能"
msgstr "Yes, but they do not have TTS functionality."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:69
#: 71a8c9e65ef74c59ae90ad4e138756d3
msgid "VC系列模组使用语音开放平台是不能进入I2C开发吗？"
msgstr ""
"Does using the voice open platform mean the VC series module cannot enter "
"I2C development?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:70
#: 760c8af495fc4989a98a3dda4870c6ef
msgid "不能开发I2C功能"
msgstr "I2C functionality cannot be developed."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:73
#: 13b089ae525f4fb792a062725802a0ed
msgid "VC系列模组支持自定义免唤醒命令词吗"
msgstr "Do VC series modules support custom wake-free command words?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:77
#: 573165c7bdc64911b044dfaceba648ef
msgid "VC系列开发板中文固件和英文固件是不是硬件通用的"
msgstr ""
"Are the Chinese firmware and English firmware for the VC series development "
"board compatible with the same hardware?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:78
#: 2eb7495647004033b235b27f214da295
msgid "共用同一个硬件"
msgstr "They use the same hardware."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:81
#: c60e2729cf1b482eb14fae998df338d0
msgid ""
"VC模组在线创建产品SDK中有B2B3B6B7引脚，但是实际产品引脚定义没有这几个引脚，是"
"怎么回事"
msgstr ""
"In the SDK created online for VC modules, there are B2, B3, B6, and B7 pins, "
"but the actual product pin definition does not include these pins. Why?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:82
#: 2d16b305e0c04977a2e0c4d0dec9a6f1
msgid ""
"B0 B1 B8 是特殊功能脚，B8是系统log 默认是输出脚波特率57600，B0 B1是JATG 烧录"
"脚"
msgstr ""
"B0, B1, and B8 are special function pins. B8 is the system log pin and is an "
"output pin by default with a baud rate of 57600. B0 and B1 are JTAG "
"programming pins."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:85
#: d1a9b9acc91b426c8d96d2bae6a70fcf
msgid "VC系列所使用的咪头参数是多少"
msgstr "What are the microphone parameters used by the VC series?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:86
#: ea6431519e0c4ee88ab2c639ade8a3cf
msgid "咪头的接收灵敏度为-31dB"
msgstr "The microphone receiving sensitivity is -31 dB."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:89
#: 1cce1ecc11ad4ae98e890535ac2dd417
msgid "VC-02模块支持永久唤醒吗"
msgstr "Does the VC-02 module support permanent wake-up?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:90
#: 7466524a7f1044778a5b1fee17d48ccd
msgid "支持，需要通过开发实现，出厂固件没有实现该功能"
msgstr ""
"Yes. It needs to be implemented through development. The factory firmware "
"does not implement this function."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:93
#: c18877078aa04293a73c0f74ac1a7bc3
msgid "请问VC语音开发板的串口是哪一种芯片？"
msgstr ""
"What chip is used for the serial port on the VC voice development board?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:94
#: 2744a03485e549cbbec02b8e6eb61a37
msgid "CH340"
msgstr "CH340."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:97
#: 93d497a3ecd04445ab9d735fb4aa3f78
msgid "VC-02-Kit是否可以用于驱动舵机？"
msgstr "Can the VC-02-Kit be used to drive a servo?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:98
#: 7e2cfe7d28dd4f5e995dbe226003d7ba
msgid "需外部搭建H桥等电路配合驱动"
msgstr "An external H-bridge or similar circuit is required for driving it."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:101
#: fa69b10821f94effb8e735626ceffcfc
msgid "目前有哪些模块支持声纹识别功能"
msgstr "Which modules currently support voiceprint recognition?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:102
#: 80fa4a14cc6245cf9fd7130efcbcfce7
msgid "声纹识别功能的模块目前没有，有语音识别的VC系列模块"
msgstr ""
"There are currently no modules with voiceprint recognition. The VC series "
"modules support voice recognition."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:105
#: df4dc12e590942d5ab722113a750f83d
msgid "VC开发板是否可以通过板子上的USB口进行固件烧录"
msgstr ""
"Can the VC development board burn firmware through the USB port on the board?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:106
#: 5db4f6f8e1474acd9932e2d63d015f54
msgid ""
"可以，模块通过USB转串口的方式给开发板进行固件烧写(烧录的固件必须使用build.sh "
"update指令生成的uni_app_release_update.bin,烧录工具只能使用UniOneUpdateTool."
"exe)"
msgstr ""
"Yes. The module uses USB-to-serial to burn firmware to the development "
"board. The firmware to be burned must be the ``uni_app_release_update.bin`` "
"generated by the ``build.sh update`` command, and the burning tool can only "
"be ``UniOneUpdateTool.exe``."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:109
#: 33c0ce98ffdf4a1ebe05bcbb98a3f1ed
msgid "VC-02的命令词可以自己编辑吗"
msgstr "Can the command words of VC-02 be edited by users?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:110
#: a7c7f541ac35475382f2b674f2a627e9
msgid "可以，通过平台生成SDK的方式"
msgstr "Yes. This can be done by generating an SDK through the platform."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:113
#: a89eb01d392e476aa1a45e4212e79caf
msgid "VC-02开发板可以同时识别英文和中文吗"
msgstr ""
"Can the VC-02 development board recognize English and Chinese at the same "
"time?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:114
#: 9933463ccc1d45ba85923834369c8509
msgid "不可以，烧写什么版本的固件就支持什么语言"
msgstr "No. It supports whichever language version of firmware is burned."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:117
#: e84a526e1df9402e815b1da4ea8d6d5a
msgid "VC-01中文和英文能做到一起使用吗"
msgstr "Can VC-01 support Chinese and English at the same time?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:118
#: 513fe5c66141412fb8574987554bfc97
msgid "不可以，中文固件和英文固件只能二选一"
msgstr ""
"No. Chinese firmware and English firmware are mutually exclusive; only one "
"can be selected."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:121
#: b5af8bd1cc764c588872334dc041e59a
msgid ""
"请问VC-02-Kit是要自己写代码么？还是给一个网页，设置完了以后生成bin文件？"
msgstr ""
"For VC-02-Kit, do users need to write code themselves, or is there a web "
"page where settings are configured and then a bin file is generated?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:122
#: 3c5281c7337745f89c823ba8bfb49537
msgid ""
"网页设置完成将生成对应功能的SDK，用户直接SDK编译完成后生成固件，也可在SDK的功"
"能做一些完善之后再编译生成固件"
msgstr ""
"After configuration on the web page, an SDK with the corresponding functions "
"will be generated. Users can directly compile the SDK to generate firmware, "
"or improve the SDK functions before compiling and generating firmware."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:125
#: 27d2da108d464052b86313771506e52c
msgid "VC-02离线语音模组可以使用arduinoIDE编程吗"
msgstr "Can the VC-02 offline voice module be programmed with Arduino IDE?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:126
#: 3a5c960e60044e9da093867f6346647a
msgid "不可以，目前仅支持通过语音平台生成的SDK进行编程"
msgstr ""
"No. Currently, it only supports programming through the SDK generated by the "
"voice platform."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:129
#: e6056f3dc25d46b0ac5ccfe8be19663d
msgid "VC-02开发板做开发的时候注册账号，下载离线语音固件需要收费吗"
msgstr ""
"When developing with the VC-02 development board, is there any charge for "
"registering an account or downloading offline voice firmware?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:130
#: d621cd4935d34320ba04887dac248520
msgid "不需要收费，注册账号和下载固件都是免费的"
msgstr "No. Account registration and firmware downloads are both free."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:133
#: a3f4d4231ea34694a5775d7b8f48cfc3
msgid "请问贵司有支持语音对话，并且可以对接云端的模组么？"
msgstr ""
"Do you have any modules that support voice conversation and cloud connection?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:134
#: b697965bbebd4914b9f5ebea9a49e434
msgid "目前没有支持语音对话的模组；"
msgstr "Currently, there are no modules that support voice conversation."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:137
#: 2541461e70054bf2b53e806dd29717d0
msgid ""
"VC系列模组通过在线生成离线语音估计，只有一个文件，没有update格式的问题该如何"
"处理"
msgstr ""
"When generating offline voice firmware online for VC series modules, only "
"one file is generated and there is no update-format file. How should this be "
"handled?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:138
#: a8a189990ab74f958d7fb27ef29c9955
msgid "使用./build.sh update，编译的时候后缀带update才会有"
msgstr ""
"Use ``./build.sh update``. The update-format file will only be generated "
"when the compilation command includes ``update``."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:141
#: 5f5cdf54cb254034b9ea5c57cd79e899
msgid "VC-02开发板配套的喇叭是多少欧姆多少W的"
msgstr ""
"What are the impedance and power rating of the speaker supplied with the "
"VC-02 development board?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:142
#: f2437777b0e64873808831946381d800
msgid "2W8欧姆"
msgstr "2W, 8 ohms."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:145
#: 333555e31eec47a980aabcd244d5cc8f
msgid "VC-02开发板支持休眠状态下进行语音唤醒吗"
msgstr "Does the VC-02 development board support voice wake-up in sleep mode?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:146
#: 2d53d483555c454a828d7a8d58501568
msgid "不支持休眠状态进行语音唤醒，目前仅支持待机状态进行语音唤醒"
msgstr ""
"It does not support voice wake-up in sleep mode. Currently, voice wake-up is "
"only supported in standby mode."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:149
#: da971ad6cfb943f2aa4db88c715dc58e
msgid "VC-02开发板可以录音吗"
msgstr "Can the VC-02 development board record audio?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:150
#: 029231f7561f403fae48fd1c0f8dac7d
msgid "不可以，开发板没有录音功能"
msgstr "No. The development board does not have a recording function."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:153
#: 7e8274e8040d4e66a66fe5cd59ce4b03
msgid "VC离线语音模组支持OTA吗"
msgstr "Does the VC offline voice module support OTA?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:154
#: 127819e5750345269e1edde565ba6118
msgid "不支持，模组本身没有这个功能"
msgstr "No. The module itself does not have this function."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:157
#: 2071fe3751bf4b6283193c374c3e7af1
msgid "请问离线语音模组输出能驱动几路继电器呢？"
msgstr "How many relay channels can the offline voice module output drive?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:158
#: ea6dd6415e384b808aaf2ffb97b2c239
msgid "4"
msgstr "4."
